## Working in this project

This project uses the `research` skill. Plans declare a category and mode; results are recorded in `plans/<id>.md` with claim structure; reports under `reports/<id>/` are the human-facing artifacts.

Research scripts should run through `new_run.py` and leave evidence under `experiments/<plan>/runs/<run_id>/`. Print-only output is not a completed result: stdout is not evidence. Each completed run needs `run_manifest.json`, `logs/stdout.log`, `logs/stderr.log`, and at least one manifest-listed durable artifact in `outputs/`, `tables/`, `figures/`, or `intermediate/`. Run `check_run_artifacts.py` before using a run for observations, claims, decisions, or reports.
